"version": "1.0.2",
"title": "8737: evil, believers' responses to",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8737: evil, believers' responses to",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture outlines several ways in which believers should respond to evil.</p>\n<h2>Evil is to be avoided</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps1:1\">PSA 1:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:14\">PRO 4:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:22\">1TH 5:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:28\">JOB 28:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:115\">PSA 119:115</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:27\">PRO 4:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:16\">PRO 14:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:11\">ISA 52:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:40\">ACT 2:40</a> <em>Peter's appeal to the crowd</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:9\">ROM 12:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:141\">ROM 13:141</a>CO <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:6-Rom5:7\">5:6–5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:9\">GAL 5:9</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:14-2Cor6:18\">2CO 6:14–6:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:27\">EPH 4:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:3\">EPH 5:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:6-Eph5:7\">EPH 5:6–5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:6\">2TH 3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:11\">1PE 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:14\">PSA 34:14</a></p>\n<h2>Evil is to be hated</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:13\">PRO 8:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:10\">PSA 97:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:15\">AMO 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:20\">JHN 3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:9\">ROM 12:9</a></p>\n<h2>Evil is to be rebuked</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:23\">MAT 16:23</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:33\">MRK 8:33</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:29\">1SA 2:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:13\">1SA 13:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:22\">1SA 15:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:9\">2SA 12:9</a> <em>Nathan rebukes David</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:18\">1KI 18:18</a> <em>Elijah rebukes Ahab</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:9\">2CH 16:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:20\">2CH 24:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr26:18\">2CH 26:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:10\">EZR 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps141:5\">PSA 141:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:27\">DAN 4:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:22\">DAN 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:4\">MAT 14:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:18\">MRK 6:18</a> <em>John the Baptist rebukes Herod</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:40\">LUK 23:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:3-Acts5:4\">ACT 5:3–5:4</a> <em>Peter rebukes Ananias</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:9\">ACT 5:9</a> <em>Peter rebukes Sapphira</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:3\">1TI 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:20\">1TI 5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:13\">TIT 1:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:15\">TIT 2:15</a></p>\n<h2>Evil is to be resisted</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:10\">PRO 1:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:11\">GAL 2:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11\">EPH 6:11</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:7\">JAS 4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:13\">1CO 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:11\">EPH 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1\">HEB 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:1\">1PE 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:9\">1PE 5:9</a></p>\n<h2>Evil is to be repaid with good</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:35\">LUK 6:35</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:20-Rom12:21\">ROM 12:20–12:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:21-Prov25:22\">PRO 25:21–25:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:5\">EXO 23:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:18\">LEV 19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:44\">MAT 5:44</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:27\">LUK 6:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess5:15\">1TH 5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:9\">1PE 3:9</a></p>\n<h2>Believers should pray in response to evil</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:13\">MAT 6:13</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:4\">LUK 11:4</a><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:29\">ACT 4:29</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:16\">HEB 4:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod17:4\">EXO 17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:36\">1KI 18:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:19\">2KI 19:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:12\">2CH 20:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra8:23\">EZR 8:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:4\">NEH 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:41\">MAT 26:41</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:38\">MRK 14:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:46\">LUK 22:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:5\">ACT 12:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:13\">JAS 5:13</a></p>\n<h2>Believers should trust God in the face of evil</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:4\">PSA 23:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:39\">MAT 26:39</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:36\">MRK 14:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:42\">LUK 22:42</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps4:8\">PSA 4:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps20:7\">PSA 20:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:1\">PSA 27:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa12:2\">ISA 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:17-Dan3:18\">DAN 3:17–3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab3:17-Hab3:18\">HAB 3:17–3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:12\">2TI 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:6\">HEB 13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:6-Ps118:7\">PSA 118:6–118:7</a></p>",
